longBusinessSummary: iTokk, Inc. does not have significant operations. Previously, it was engaged in the provision of voice-over-Internet protocol (VOIP) and related products and services in North America and Europe. The company was formerly known as Shadow Marketing Inc. and changed its name to itokk, Inc. in October 2009. iTokk, Inc. was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
